description: Fusion cuisine like you've never seen before is right around the corner, with Ben and Ollie's Navajo Tacos and Sweet Frybread! Bringing together their Polynesian family recipes with the amazing taste of Native American frybread, this truck has an amazing menu you're sure to love. Whether you're looking for a sweet or savory treat, these fine folks have you covered!
name: Ben and Ollie's Navajo Tacos and Sweet Frybread
